‘I am saying no because it is alright for me to take time off for myself and for my daughter. I want to give her my undivided attention.’

And with the date for the richest fight in ring history fast approaching, Mayweather says his preparations are going well.

He added: ‘The training camp has been good. I’m happy and I’m pretty sure my father is happy and everything is great.’

 

